This paper investigates the delivery of personalized ads by Google AdSense, which involves the use of algorithms and data analysis. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CY). The paper also involves the analysis of search results and the use of machine learning techniques, which are relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to bias and discrimination, which are relevant to Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) and Software Engineering (cs.SD).
